        • awards

          java.util.Set<E> contracts
          Contracts

          Information from the contract creation phase of the procurement process.

        • language

          java.lang.String language
          Release language

          Specifies the default language of the data using either two-letter [ISO639-1](https://en.wikipedia .org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes), or extended [BCP47 language tags](http://www .w3.org/International/articles/language-tags/). The use of lowercase two-letter codes from [ISO639-1] (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes) is strongly recommended.

          java.util.Set<E> relatedProcesses
